   "source": [
    "## Solution\n",
    "\n",
    "We can handle it with string\n",
    "\n",
    "judge the palindrome by comparing the num and the reverse of num\n",
    "\n",
    "use slicing to reverse a string or list: '[::-1]'\n",
    "\n",
    "if it is negative, remove the '-'"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "num = input()\n",
    "if num[0]=='-':\n",
    "    num = num[1:]\n",
    "print(num == num[::-1])"
   ]
  }
